Const SubscriptionValidationResponse

SubscriptionValidationResponse: object
  • Defined in models/index.ts:774
  • Defined in models/mappers.ts:982
interface

An interface representing SubscriptionValidationResponse. To complete an event subscription validation handshake, a subscriber can use either the validationCode or the validationUrl received in a SubscriptionValidationEvent. When the validationCode is used, the SubscriptionValidationResponse can be used to build the response.
